data.description: Discover the inviting charm of this spacious home in East Terrell Hills! With 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a roomy living area, it's perfect for any lifestyle. Enjoy easy access to I-35 and 410, nearby parks, and just a short 10-minute drive to SAMMC. Home has just been refreshed with paint throughout, new water heater, new blinds, and all appliances convey with the purchase! Situated in a quiet cul-de-sac for added privacy. Don't miss out on making this home yours!
